name: Aratech Corporation
Lore: 'Aratech Corporation sent support staff to various Imperial outposts and garrisons. Gave advanced briefings and training to biker scout personnel.',
Text: 'Deploy on Carida system. Your speeder bikes piloted by biker scouts are power +1 and forfeit +1 and may follow (for free) an opponent''s vehicle or character that just moved from same site (if within range). (Immune to Alter while you occupy Carida.)',
